      "writtenOn": "2020-08-06T06:05:47Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I\u0027d bet this is where all the time is burned. If dep.Key was an index of a CL in a cls list, then this wouldn\u0027t be a problem.\nThis can be pre-computed in O(E). In fact, CLs themselves can be identified by index, too.\n\nLet\u0027s not do this yet in this CL, but please add a TODO somewhere in code to do this once we define internally a CL for CQ.",
      "range": {
